 config I2C_ISA
 	tristate "ISA Bus support"
-	depends on I2C && EXPERIMENTAL
+	depends on I2C && ISA && EXPERIMENTAL
 	help
 	  If you say yes to this option, support will be included for i2c
 	  interfaces that are on the ISA bus.